# This cron runs scripts provided by python-slogging
# to gather some statistics and then upload them to 
# an account on the cluster itself 
# Only enable the below if python-slogging has been 
# installed and configured properly
#
# Storage - Account stats
##0 * * * * swift swift-account-stats-logger /etc/swift/log-processor.conf
##20 * * * * swift swift-log-uploader /etc/swift/log-processor.conf stats
# Storage - Container stats
##20 * * * * swift swift-container-stats-logger /etc/swift/log-processor.conf
##40 * * * * swift swift-log-uploader /etc/swift/log-processor.conf container-stats
